{"prompt": "Generate a website for a online magazine. The website should be modern and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Modern Online Magazine</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935;\n            --secondary-color: #fce4ec;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-footer-bg: #f8bbd0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.7), rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1200x400/e53935/ffffff?text=Featured+Article') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 4rem 2rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .articles {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .article-card {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border: 1px solid #eeeeee;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .article-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .article-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .article-content {\n            padding: 1rem;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .article-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .article-content p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .read-more {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: auto;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .read-more:hover {\n            background-color: #c62828;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n\n            .hero-section h2 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n            }\n\n            nav a {\n                margin: 0 0.5rem;\n                font-size: 0.9rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>The Modern Chronicle</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#latest\">Latest</a>\n        <a href=\"#features\">Features</a>\n        <a href=\"#opinion\">Opinion</a>\n        <a href=\"#culture\">Culture</a>\n        <a href=\"#tech\">Tech</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\n        <section class=\"hero-section\">\n            <h2>Unveiling Tomorrow's Trends Today</h2>\n            <p>Dive into insightful articles, breaking news, and diverse perspectives shaping our world.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"latest\">\n            <h2>Latest Articles</h2>\n            <div class=\"articles\">\n                <article class=\"article-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/fce4ec/e53935?text=Article+1\" alt=\"Article 1 Image\">\n                    <div class=\"article-content\">\n                        <h3>The Future of Sustainable Cities</h3>\n                        <p>Exploring innovative urban planning and eco-friendly living solutions for a greener tomorrow.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </article>\n                <article class=\"article-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/fce4ec/e53935?text=Article+2\" alt=\"Article 2 Image\">\n                    <div class=\"article-content\">\n                        <h3>AI's Impact on Creative Industries</h3>\n                        <p>How artificial intelligence is revolutionizing art, music, and writing, and what it means for creators.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </article>\n                <article class=\"article-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/fce4ec/e53935?text=Article+3\" alt=\"Article 3 Image\">\n                    <div class=\"article-content\">\n                        <h3>Navigating the Digital Nomad Lifestyle</h3>\n                        <p>Tips and insights for embracing remote work and exploring the world simultaneously.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More</a>\n                    </div>\n                </article>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"features\" style=\"margin-top: 3rem;\">\n            <h2>Featured Stories</h2>\n            <div class=\"articles\">\n                <article class=\"article-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/fce4ec/e53935?text=Feature+1\" alt=\"Feature 1 Image\">\n                    <div class=\"article-content\">\n                        <h3>Deep Dive: Quantum Computing Breakthroughs</h3>\n                        <p>Understanding the complex world of quantum computing and its potential to change everything.</p>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"read-more\">Read More</a>\n        